name: Baarbara Coffee's Roasted Arabica Coffee Beans + Vienna Dark Roasted Coffee Beans
description:
• Savour the full-bodied flavours of our AA-Grade 100% Roasted Arabica beans with long-lasting, pleasant taste with a delicate flavour and a balanced aroma.

  • Start your day with the distinctive flavour of our Vienna Dark Coffee Roast. This full-bodied brew boasts high to low acidity and provides an intense and enriching coffee taste that will thrill any coffee enthusiast. 

  • Elevate Your Mornings with our Premium Coffee Pairing
